Trade/Device Name(s): LIAISON® 25 OH Vitamin D TOTAL Calibration Verifiers
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for DiaSorin LIAISON 25 OH Vitamin D TOTAL Calibration Verifiers as assayed quality control materials for the LIAISON 25 OH Vitamin D TOTAL Assay.
Indications for Use Summary: Assayed quality control materials intended for in vitro diagnostic use in the quantitative verification of calibration and reportable range of the LIAISON 25 OH Vitamin D TOTAL Assay when performed on the LIAISON Analyzer.
